title: Beautiful 1 Bedroom For Rent
posting_body: ['Apartment Features:', '- Stained dark hardwood floors', '- Granite counter tops, breakfast bar and white hardwood cabinetry', '- Full size white appliances including: dishwasher, microwave, stove and fridge', '- Bathroom with marble tiling, contemporary fixtures and bathtub', '- Central HVAC (heat and air conditioning are tenant paid and controlled)', '- Ample closet space with custom fit organizers', '- Pet friendly (dogs up to 40lbs)', '- On-site laundry', '- Outdoor, assigned parking available', '- Shared yard', 'In Lincoln Park, Chicago\'s "City in a Garden"—truly comes to life.', 'Historic churches and handsome brick row houses nestled within landmark districts sit next to peaceful parks, while quiet, tree-lined residential areas give way to bustling business corridors.', 'If interested, please text Natalie at 312-637-0853 for the fastest response to schedule a showing.', 'The building is managed by Kass Management.', 'Thank you!']
